title: The Annual AFC Over-Unders With Cousin Sal | The Bill Simmons Podcast (Ep. 407)
description:
In part one of their two-part podcast, HBO and The Ringer's Bill Simmons and Cousin Sal gear up for the NFL regular season by running thru each team in the AFC, they talk odds, sleepers, parlays, and more!
